description: The investment objective of Lyxor Index Fund Lyxor Stoxx Europe 600 Technology UCITS ETF (the Sub-Fund) is to track the upward and the downward evolution of the STOXX Europe 600 Technology Net Total Return (the Index) denominated in Euros and representative of the performance of large European companies in the technology sector.
name: Lyxor Index Fund - Lyxor STOXX Europe 600 Technology UCITS ETF
